D4:1.5 R:0.5 D4:0.75@0.4 R:1.25 C4:1.5 R:0.5 C4:0.75@0.4 R:1.25
A3:1.5 R:0.5 A3:0.75@0.4 R:1.25 E3:1.5 R:0.5 E3:0.75@0.4 R:1.25
D3:3 R:1 D3:1@0.3 R:3

track beat kit=909
>8
